Quote:  There is one thing, however, that I am not quite pleased with - that is, that the Building Committee should have been entirely chosen from among the big wigs of the district, as I should have liked to see them joined by a few of my own class - that is, tussockers, ditchers, or other decent and respectable farm labourers.
